  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_newspaper_2a6b4fa088699701a6fa9ccecfb5c25d_18_17",
    "text": "The 2016 fl athead sole and yellowfin sole CDQ reserves specified in the BSAI are 1,617 metric tons (mt), and 16,933 mt as established by the final 2016 and 2017 harvest specifications for groundfish in the BSAI (81 FR 14773, March 18, 2016) and following revision (81 FR 64782, September 21, 2016). The 2016 fl athead sole and yellowfin sole CDQ ABC reserves are 5,472 mt and 5,719 mt as established by the final 2016 and 2017 harvest specifications for gundfish in the BSAI (81 FR14773 March 18, 2016) and following revision (81 FR 64782, September 21, 2016).",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
